<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='476000' id='t-476000'>Where are we today?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='477000' id='t-477000'>That's year by year. This comes from our friends at Gapminder.com.</span>
