</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:44
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='513000' id='t-513000'>As a matter of fact, we think reaching 100 percent is very doable,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='517000' id='t-517000'>even before the 2015 timeframe. In other parts of emerging countries,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='523000' id='t-523000'>such as India and China, the progress has been good --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='526000' id='t-526000'>has been solid, has been good. But in places that are not as developed,</span>
