<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='626000' id='t-626000'>from being able to be connected to the Internet.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='629000' id='t-629000'>Therefore, when we see that, we see an opportunity</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='632000' id='t-632000'>to have a business that addresses the need of that segment.</span>
