<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='674000' id='t-674000'>It is an initiative that is focused on simple, accessible and human-centric solutions.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='678000' id='t-678000'>What we mean by that is,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='680000' id='t-680000'>you know, frankly, the PC was invented in 1980, roughly speaking</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='684000' id='t-684000'>more or less, and for 20-odd years, it hasn't changed.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='689000' id='t-689000'>It is still, in most places, a gray or black box, and it looks the same.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='694000' id='t-694000'>And frankly -- and I know that sometimes I offend some of my customers</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='698000' id='t-698000'>when I say this, but I truly mean it --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='700000' id='t-700000'>if you could take the name of the computer off the top of it,</span>
