<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='729000' id='t-729000'>And it has to be based on a geo-sensitive approach.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='731000' id='t-731000'>What I mean by that is that in some parts of the world,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='734000' id='t-734000'>the government plays a key role in the development of technology.</span>
