<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='821000' id='t-821000'>I don't think this segment of the market can be addressed</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='824000' id='t-824000'>by companies parachuting from another place of the world,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='828000' id='t-828000'>and just dumping product and selling into the markets.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='830000' id='t-830000'>So, we believe that in those regions of the world</span>
