<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='936000' id='t-936000'>One example of this has been the One Laptop per Child.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='939000' id='t-939000'>Some of you are familiar with this.</span>
